node.text: i love how you sing when you hear music. i love how you always ask if everyone’s happy. i love how when other kids are around you ask them if they want to play with you. i love how you love all the coolest things like dinosaurs & bugs. i love when i’m taking a bath and you ask to crawl in with me & we lay there laughing at eachother. i love when you tell me bed time stories & they always surprise me. i love that everyone showers you with complements and your eyes light up. i love how funny you are Dey. i love your love. forever and ever we go Bear. photo by tt jamie @_jamiejamster 🤍

node.text: hopppped out the matrix n i hopped in my bag! yeah. i’m workin on projects i am in love wit.. putting on so many hats. i finished alottttta music i wanted/needed to finish.. it’s comin. my production company is about to have a stellar first year, so many surprises in the works. i’m utterly mindblown consistently at what comes of hard work, & tending to spirit. standing on the shoulders of those who came before me, putting in real work to develop insightful connection… and keepin my ears transparently open. i’m not as wordy as i use to be but i can tell you this.. my mind is at its sharpest, my heart at its fullest, my spirit at its most honest and my curiosity is through the roof. im loving and loved. couldn’t nothing top this… except when all i’m planting comes to bloom.. but im really fuckin lovin laying the seeds in the ground. just tappin in to say i love you n thank you. iss forever gon be a Honey thang 🍯
